        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Add </strong>the<strong>&nbsp;</strong>onion to the potato tray&nbsp;with an extra drizzle of oil</p> <p><strong>Place</strong>&nbsp;the tray back in the oven until the end of the next step</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/melty-blue-cheese-pork-steak-with-pears/step-4.jpg"
